# Sophie's container env. Intentionally minimal — no GH_TOKEN, no git identity.
# Sophie does not commit code; she writes notes that Nick syncs from the host.

# Google Workspace CLI (`gws`) — OAuth client credentials.
# Create a Desktop OAuth app at https://console.cloud.google.com/apis/credentials,
# enable the Workspace APIs you want, then drop the client ID/secret here.
# After this is set, run `gws auth login` once inside Sophie's container.
GOOGLE_WORKSPACE_CLI_CLIENT_ID=
GOOGLE_WORKSPACE_CLI_CLIENT_SECRET=
